This paper is about personalized product search, which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR) in computer science. Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses neural networks to learn and integrate user preferences, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV), so cs.CL and cs.CV are also likely sub-categories.
